data.description: You will never run out of storage w/ this 3116sqft, 3BD, 3.5BA home, and a garage that can fit 4 vehicles located in sought after Seymour. Beautiful open floor plan on main floor with kitchen flowing into the dining and living room. This home offers two possible master bedrooms with full bathrooms upstairs and down. Covered front porch has been extended and rebuilt. The walkout basement into the back yard on the patio offers an enormous area for entertainment and cookouts. Owners also are including a home warranty. Schedule your private showing today!
